songs.content:
Tulumbanishe maka ye
   Shina lya kwa Yesu;
Abangeli na bantu fye,

        Balumbanye shina,
        ‘Shina lya kwa Yesu.

Abafwile balumbanye
   ‘Wanina ku mulu;
Wa kwi shinte lya kwa Yese,

Abasumina pano nse,
   Abwa balubuka;
Na ‘baetulwa no luse,

Abelelwa te kulaba
   Ifyo aculile;
Bamuletelele ubupe,

Abena fyalo ba ndimi
Shonse sha pano nse;
Balete kuno mucinshi,
n Ba no nse, ba mu mulu,
Bonse bamuwile;
Bembe ulwimbo lumo fye,

Mwe Mupashi wa Luse,
Leka mbe we luse ‘ne;
Na mashiwi ya kwafwa
Muli ne yamoneke;
No kushipa ne congwe
Kansose fya kwa Kristu.

Mwe Mupashi wa Cine,
Leka mbe wa cine ‘ne;
Mbe na mano yafula,
Ya kumulumbanisha;
Ne micitile yandi
‘Kuti imubombele.

Mwe Mupashi Mufuke,
Kambyo mufuke ine;
Kanjisalyo mutima
Ilyo esa katunka;
No kwisula pa numa,
‘Kuti mubalikemo.

Mwe Mupashi Tondolo,
Tondolo kanjikale;
‘Fintwi cani cakula,
Ku mushily catula;
Ngo lubutwa kacelo
Ulufumya impepo.

Mwe Mupashi wa Maka,
Aya yene ndefwaya;
‘Kuti nkose nshiku pe,
Te ku maka yandi fye;
Ubucetekelo bu
Bukamfisha ku mulu.

Mwe Mupashi Wabuta,
Ine kamupashanye.
Mumpatule ku fibi,
Nsale fisuma fyeka;
Mungafwe ‘kuti mpele
Fyandi fyonse kuli ‘mwe.

Ndefwaya kwimbe inshita pe,
    ‘Filamba fyafutwa;
Ndi cibusa wakwa Yesu,
    Nalamubombela.

        Ndamulumbanya,
             Mulumbanya pe;
        Mulumbanya,
             Ndamulumbanya pe;

‘Kumumona pa lupanda,
    Uko atanikilwe;
Nalilishe ifilamba,
    Nomba mulumbanya.

Nga natunkwa na matunko,
    Nalamwibukisha;
Nelyo nsakamikwako
    Nalamulumbanya.

Ne landwe ilya kwa Yesu
    Nakulashimika;
Bambi babulyo lwimbo lu
    Lwa kumulumbanya.

Tata, mumfwe bamwano,
Tulelomba ilelo.
Twamulwila mwi pepo;
    Twapapata mumfwe.

Yesu, ‘lupanda lwenu
Lwafumye fibi fyesu;
Twimbile shina lyenu;
    Twapapata mumfwe.

Mwe Mupashi wa mweo,
Ifwe tatuli bwino,
Tulelosha ilel;
    Twpapata mufwe.

‘Luse lwatufyalilwe,
‘Luse lwatufwilile,
‘Luse lwatupuseishe;
    Twapapata mumfwe.

Ifyo ndi-nshitelebwila,
Umulopa wansumina;
Kuli imwe, mwe banjita,
   Mwe Mfumu naisa.

Ifyo ndi-nshilepembela
‘Kufumya cimo cabipa;
Kuli ‘mwe mwe ba unsamba,
   Mwe Mfumu naisa.

Ifyo ndi-mwalinjishiba,
Napenampena ne fingi,
‘Kulwishanya mu mutima;
   Mwe Mfumu naisa.

Ifyo ndi-‘mupina, ‘mpofu;
Kampoke fyuma fya mpomfu;
‘Kwa kufisanga ni kwenu;
   Mwe Mfumu naisa.

Ifyo ndi-mwampokelela,
‘Kunjelela no kunsamba,
‘Fyo mwalaya nasumina;
   Mwe Mfumu naisa.

Ifyo ndi-‘kutemwa kwenu
Kwayanshe filwani bwangu;
Nomba mwe Mfumu ndi wenu;
Mwe Mfumu naisa.

“E mubili wandyu yo napela;
    Citeni ci no kunjibukisha”;
‘Mwana wa mpanga, ilambo ni ‘mwe,
    Ni mwe mukate wesu wa mweo.

“E mulopa wandyu wasumine”
    -Asosa fi, apisho lukombo;
Ifyo fine, tunwe ifwe bene,
    Tummfwo buseko ubwaisapo.

“Nshita yaise,” fyo asosele;
    Mwikale ne fwe, fwe bo Mwatemwa;
Mututebete ‘muku ‘no wine,
    Apo tamulasendwa kuli ‘few.

‘Mfifi ya cungulo ilepona,
    ‘Bulanda mu mitima twaumfwa;
Twaimbo lwimbo lwa kulekana,
    Twaumfwa ‘ti, “Imeni tuleya.”
